{"tid":1132423,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"頸椎有問題，想買枕頭，求請教","createTime":"2019-04-30T09:47:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T12:54:22.000Z","uid":158055,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6b9901f0ba0473ced698c5b4924eb4affe616df9","tid":1132423,"uid":158055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T09:47:09.000Z","msg":"小弟條頸椎有事，生理曲度強直左<br />\n大約係咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/04/30/165156_01478a210906d8977149f22817e07a23.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F04%2F30%2F165156_01478a210906d8977149f22817e07a23.png&h=55464764&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n肩緊頸痛<br />\n咁小弟個枕頭係好普通果啲黎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n近排想買個矯型枕，頂到條頸，枕頭中間係凹果啲，<br />\n睇啱sinomax同tempur依4款<br />\n亦都試左，舒服但感覺差唔多<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FRaaJXF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFRaaJXF.png&h=75c35449&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U1RQJXH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU1RQJXH.png&h=827e46b4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y2RJjv4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY2RJjv4.png&h=660726e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前都去宜家試過依隻<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/04/30/173026_ef30b5e5b68004816d30e69ab51396aa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F04%2F30%2F173026_ef30b5e5b68004816d30e69ab51396aa.png&h=d1a94c78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上網都睇過依隻，講到好似好勁咁，但我實際未試過<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LxV2AhJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLxV2AhJ.png&h=2e46e9c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想問有冇師兄有用開依啲枕頭？因為我覺得枕頭依啲真係要長用先知係點，或者有咩其他牌子都可以推薦下，唔該曬各位"},{"pid":"404e97ca106b3a0ced627b6202f713447fefc1c4","tid":1132423,"uid":22362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T09:48:43.000Z","msg":"最簡單買圓柱型頸枕<br />\n淨係枕條頸"},{"pid":"945cc8dd3d9851cb2389dd46b7184973583b37df","tid":1132423,"uid":158055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"404e97ca106b3a0ced627b6202f713447fefc1c4","tid":1132423,"uid":22362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T09:48:43.000Z","msg":"最簡單買圓柱型頸枕<br />\n淨係枕條頸"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T09:51:12.000Z","msg":"之前都有上網睇話咩捲毛巾枕頸<br />\n試左幾日，個後尾枕好唔舒服<br />\n因為張床好硬。。。"},{"pid":"0f14ccc033d13a034285f92f641d700a87933329","tid":1132423,"uid":22362,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T09:51:27.000Z","msg":"示意圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O1MUrrL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO1MUrrL.png&h=101f6547&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"56441f9a7a7f225a6b433680aea34c7bcb20f10d","tid":1132423,"uid":158055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T09:51:44.000Z","msg":"小弟翻工先喇，晏啲覆"},{"pid":"2f2af63e11e752d9715c3bfa872f5308cf08cc8a","tid":1132423,"uid":158055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f14ccc033d13a034285f92f641d700a87933329","tid":1132423,"uid":22362,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T09:51:27.000Z","msg":"示意圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O1MUrrL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO1MUrrL.png&h=101f6547&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T09:52:11.000Z","msg":"我明白呀"},{"pid":"426964d91fb3554abb53b2afcf55eb6475f4a8a2","tid":1132423,"uid":22362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"945cc8dd3d9851cb2389dd46b7184973583b37df","tid":1132423,"uid":158055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"404e97ca106b3a0ced627b6202f713447fefc1c4","tid":1132423,"uid":22362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T09:48:43.000Z","msg":"最簡單買圓柱型頸枕<br />\n淨係枕條頸"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T09:51:12.000Z","m